<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Letter Book Copy: letters copied into a bound letter-book ]">LB</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>.
</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0111-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0111-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0098" class="document">St. Clair to GW, 20 April</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0103&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-05-02-0103-fn-0001#GEWN-02-05-02-0103-fn-0001" class="document">GW to John Blair, 24 April, n.1</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0111-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0111-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>This paragraph ends in the letter book: but the nature of these people is such as induces them to retire with their <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">first</span> scalps.</p>

</div>
